HashSet vs TreeSet
1️⃣ HashSet stores elements in random order, while TreeSet stores elements in sorted order.

2️⃣ HashSet uses Hash Table, while TreeSet uses Red-Black Tree.

3️⃣ HashSet is faster, while TreeSet is slightly slower because it maintains sorting.


